@startuml
title Master Data Import To Organization Products

|Admin User|
start
:Open product import or creation screen;
:Search/select master category or product;

|Admin Frontend|
:Request master data records;

|Backend /master-data|
:Read master category, product, variant, price, vendor, bundle records;
:Return selected master data;

|Admin User|
:Confirm import into organization;

|Backend /admin or /super-admin|
:Validate organization context;
if (Product already imported by referenceId?) then (Yes)
  :Load existing organization product;
else (No)
  :Create organization product with referenceId;
endif

if (Category reference exists?) then (No)
  :Create organization category reference;
else (Yes)
endif

if (Vendor reference exists?) then (No)
  :Create organization vendor reference;
else (Yes)
endif

:Create or update variants from master variants;
:Create or update prices from master prices;

if (Master product is bundle?) then (Yes)
  :Create bundle item references;
else (No)
endif

:Initialize stock records when required;

|Database|
:Persist organization-local product data;

|Backend /admin or /super-admin|
:Return imported product result;

|Admin User|
:Review product in organization catalog;
stop
@enduml
